CONTENT RULES:
- All text must be in English
- Labels: sentence case (not ALL CAPS)
  e.g. "FCFS slots" not "FCFS SLOTS"
  e.g. "Reward / winner" not "REWARD / WINNER"
  e.g. "Claim fee" not "CLAIM FEE"
- Dates: compact format "Jun 15, 21:39"
- Numbers: always show unit "1 CC" "3 tasks"
- Empty states: show "—" not blank

